.panel
  .top-bar
    .title Guest Names
  p(style="margin-bottom: 1em; font-size:0.8em; color: #555;") If no guest data currently exists, just click save
  form(name="form" novalidate)
    .field(ng-repeat="guest in guestList")
      input(type="text" placeholder="Guest Name" autofocus ng-model="guest.name")
    .field.right
      button.grey.outline(ng-click="addNewGuestName()")
        i.icon-thin-251_plus_add
        span Add Guest Name
  hr
  .modal-footer
    button.dark-accent.full(ng-click="save()") Save